00:34:36,320 --> 00:34:38,900
但在外面不是
but not outside.

192
00:34:38,990 --> 00:34:40,990
我不明白
I do not understand.

193
00:34:41,070 --> 00:34:44,160
外面是个民国
Outside China is now a republic...

194
00:34:44,240 --> 00:34:46,240
还有个总统
with a president.

195
00:34:47,370 --> 00:34:49,580
嬷嬷在哪儿？
Where is Ar Mo?

196
00:34:51,170 --> 00:34:53,170
嬷嬷？
Ar Mo.

197
00:35:14,570 --> 00:35:17,070
你们都是骗子！
You are all liars!

198
00:35:23,700 --> 00:35:26,620
让我跟他道别！ 快！快！
- Let me say good-bye! - Hurry. Hurry.

199
00:35:31,540 --> 00:35:33,630
他是我的孩子！
He's my child!

200
00:35:51,730 --> 00:35:55,770
阿嬷？
Ar Mo?

201
00:36:06,030 --> 00:36:10,910
我不明白
I do not understand.

202
00:36:11,000 --> 00:36:15,710
皇上现在是个大孩子了 不该再有奶妈了
Your Majesty is a big boy now. He cannot have a wet nurse anymore

203
00:36:15,790 --> 00:36:17,790
这样好多了
It is much better like this.

204
00:36:17,880 --> 00:36:20,010
健康多了
Much healthier.

205
00:36:20,090 --> 00:36:22,720
但她不是我的奶妈
But she is not my wet nurse.

206
00:36:23,760 --> 00:36:26,390
她是我的蝴蝶
She is my buttefrly.

207
00:36:38,690 --> 00:37:12,810
阿嬷！
Ar Mo!

208
00:37:58,020 --> 00:38:01,150
这是感化中心
This is the detention center...

209
00:38:01,230 --> 00:38:04,860
位于公共安全抚顺局
of the Fushun Bureau of Public Security.

210
00:38:04,940 --> 00:38:07,610
我是这里的主管！
And I am the governor.

211
00:38:07,700 --> 00:38:11,530
战争期间  这里是日本的监狱
During the war, this was aJapanese prison

212
00:38:11,620 --> 00:38:13,830
你们大部分可能还记得
Many ofyou may remember it..

213
00:38:13,910 --> 00:38:16,960
因为你们为日本人工作
because you worked with the Japanese

214
00:38:17,040 --> 00:38:19,460
你们要为它的建成负责
You were responsible for building it..

215
00:38:19,540 --> 00:38:22,290
你们还关满了无辜的人
and you filled it with innocent people

216
00:38:22,380 --> 00:38:24,170
怎么会这样呢？
How could this happen?

217
00:38:24,260 --> 00:38:26,550
为什么你们背叛自己的国家？！
Why did you betray your country?

218
00:38:26,630 --> 00:38:29,180
为什么你们会变成战犯呢？
What turned you into war criminals?

219
00:38:29,260 --> 00:38:33,140
我们相信人生来本性是好的
We believe that men are born good.

220
00:38:33,220 --> 00:38:39,060
我们相信改变的唯一方法就是 找出真相 直接面对它
We believe that the only way to change is to discover the truth and look at it in the face.

221
00:38:40,310 --> 00:38:42,940
这就是你们在这里的原因
That is why you are here

222
00:38:43,020 --> 00:38:46,780
你们先要交待清楚生平情况
You will begin by writing the story of your lives...

223
00:38:46,860 --> 00:38:49,150
并坦承罪行
and by confessing your crimes

224
00:38:49,240 --> 00:38:55,160
能否赎罪取决于你们所抱的态度
Your salvation will lie entirely in the attitude you take.

225
00:38:55,240 --> 00:38:59,660
我提议你们要坦诚真挚
I advise you to be frank and sincere

226
00:38:59,750 --> 00:39:04,710
不然，你们不会好过
otherwise, things can still go very badly for you.

227
00:39:30,740 --> 00:39:32,700
几年后…
After a few years...

228
00:39:32,780 --> 00:39:36,240
民国和清末同样腐败
the Chinese Republic had become as corrupt as the old empire.

229
00:39:36,330 --> 00:39:42,290
很快便由军阀及官僚把持
It fell quickly into the hands of ambitious generals and corrupt bureaucrats.

230
00:39:42,380 --> 00:39:45,670
军阀割据时代开始
The era of the warlords had begun

231
00:39:45,750 --> 00:39:50,720
l9l9年5月我获任命时 中国正动荡不安
By May 1919, when I received my appointment, China was in turmoil

232
00:41:57,130 --> 00:41:59,760
皇上，师傅勤见
May the new tutor present himself.

233
00:42:15,240 --> 00:42:18,200
皇上 新师傅来了
Your Imperial Highness, the new tutor.

234
00:42:20,530 --> 00:42:23,370
雷金纳德・费兰芒・庄士敦先生
Mr. Reginald Fleming Johnston

235
00:42:24,540 --> 00:42:26,790
你好 庄士敦先生
How do you do, Mr.Johnston?

236
00:42:26,870 --> 00:42:30,500
你好 皇上
How do you do, Your Majesty?

237
00:42:41,100 --> 00:42:43,300
我们上课吧
Now we will go to school.

238
00:42:44,770 --> 00:42:47,890
皇上 在我的国家  一般要
Your Majesty, in my country, it would be usual to begin...

239
00:42:47,980 --> 00:42:50,350
先考试一下
with some kind ofan examination.

240
00:42:51,560 --> 00:42:53,860
皇帝不能被考
The emperor cannot be examined.

241
00:42:53,940 --> 00:42:56,070
好吧 那只好改一下
Well, that may have to change.

242
00:42:56,150 --> 00:43:00,490
可是 皇上或许想问我一些问题
But first Your Majesty might like to ask me some questions.

243
00:43:04,160 --> 00:43:06,080
你的祖先在哪儿？
Where are your ancestors buried?

244
00:43:06,160 --> 00:43:08,160
苏格兰 皇上
In Scotland, Your Majesty.

245
00:43:10,790 --> 00:43:13,290
那么 你不穿裙子？
But then, where's your skirt?

246
00:43:13,380 --> 00:43:16,300
在你们国家 男人穿短裙子 不是吗？
In your country, men wear short skirts, do they not?

247
00:43:16,380 --> 00:43:21,550
不是 皇上 苏格兰人不穿裙子 他们穿方格呢短裙
No, Your Majesty. Scotsmen do not wear skirts. They wear kilts.

248
00:43:21,640 --> 00:43:24,350
方格呢短裙？ 方格呢短裙
- Kilts? - Kilts.

249
00:43:24,430 --> 00:43:28,310
或许只是一个措词的问题  但是措词非常重要
A matter of words, perhaps, but words are important.

250
00:43:28,390 --> 00:43:30,560
为什么措词重要？
Why are words important?

251
00:43:30,640 --> 00:43:35,730
如果你不能说出你的本意 皇上 那你就不会说话算数了
If you cannot say what you mean, Your Majesty, you will never mean what you say...

252
00:43:35,820 --> 00:43:39,820
一个绅士应该永远说话算数
and a gentleman should always mean what he says.

253
00:43:39,900 --> 00:43:43,620
是的！“绅士” 
Ah, yes. A gentleman.

254
00:43:43,700 --> 00:43:45,700
你是绅士吗？
Are you a gentleman?

255
00:43:46,790 --> 00:43:50,410
我非常想做绅士 皇上
I would like to be a gentleman, Your Majesty.

256
00:43:50,500 --> 00:43:53,790
- 我努力去做 - 朕不是绅士
- I try to be. - I am not a gentleman.

257
00:43:53,880 --> 00:43:56,000
朕被禁止说心里话
I'm not allowed to say what I mean.

258
00:43:56,090 --> 00:43:58,550
他们常告诉朕该说些什么
They are always telling me what to say.

259
00:44:00,300 --> 00:44:03,220
皇上尚年轻
Your Majesty is still very young.

260
00:44:05,890 --> 00:44:10,390
皇上也许想看看英、美杂志
I thought he might like to see some English and American magazines.

261
00:44:10,480 --> 00:44:14,060
是我刚收到的
I have just received them.

262
00:44:19,280 --> 00:44:21,900
我知道你所知道的
I know that you know that I know..

263
00:44:21,990 --> 00:44:24,660
我知道的你所知的
that you know that that is a dialogue...

264
00:44:24,740 --> 00:44:27,330
那是孔子和庄子之间的对话
between Confucius and Chuang-Tsu.

265
00:44:28,330 --> 00:44:32,160
注意尊严 皇上
Concerning respect, Your Majesty.

266
00:44:46,300 --> 00:44:48,680
谁是“乔治.华盛顿”？
Who is this George washington?

267
00:44:48,760 --> 00:44:50,850
一个著名的美国人 皇上
A famous American, Your Majesty.

268
00:44:50,930 --> 00:44:55,020
一个革命的将军 美国第一任总统
A Revolutionary general. The first American president.

269
00:44:55,100 --> 00:44:57,480
噢！象苏联的列宁先生？
Ah. Like Mr. Lenin in Russia?

270
00:44:58,480 --> 00:45:01,110
不太一样
Not quite.

271
00:45:01,190 --> 00:45:03,900
他有车吗？
Does he have a car?

272
00:45:03,990 --> 00:45:06,950
他去世很久了 皇上
He lived a long time ago, Your Majesty.

273
00:45:08,200 --> 00:45:10,200
我想要辆车
I want a car.

274
00:45:15,080 --> 00:45:19,090
我认为你的老鼠想逃掉 皇上
I think your mouse is trying to escape Your Majesty.

275
00:45:23,050 --> 00:45:25,630
别把老鼠这秘密告诉别人
Please do not tell anyone about my mouse.

276
00:45:36,190 --> 00:45:38,810
下课了
The lesson is finished.

277
00:46:10,140 --> 00:46:13,180
尝膳的太监是个勇敢的人
The official taster's a brave man

278
00:46:14,600 --> 00:46:17,190
先帝有不少是被毒害的
Many of my ancestors have been poisoned, you know.

279
00:46:21,060 --> 00:46:24,360
皇上每天如此进午膳的吗?
Does Your Majesty have lunch like this every day?

280
00:46:24,440 --> 00:46:26,900
对 每天如是 像做马戏似的
Ah, yes. Every day. Like theater.

281
00:46:26,990 --> 00:46:29,860
朕不知何原因，一向如是
I do not know why. It has always been like that

282
00:46:35,200 --> 00:46:37,540
在西方是如何杀害帝王的?
How do they kill emperors in the West?

283
00:46:39,710 --> 00:46:42,590
奥国皇帝给枪杀，是吗?
The Austrian emperor was shot was he not?

284
00:46:42,670 --> 00:46:46,800
不是 不过他的侄儿大战前给暗杀
No. But his nephew was assassinated before the Great War.

285
00:46:46,880 --> 00:46:50,130
但俄国沙皇就给枪杀了
But the Russian emperor has been shot. He was called a czar.

286
00:46:50,220 --> 00:46:51,840
是的
Yes.

287
00:46:51,930 --> 00:46:54,810
他侵占满州不少地方
He took lots ofour land in Manchuria.

288
00:46:54,890 --> 00:46:58,940
朕是满州人 甚至民国以后，满州仍是朕的国土
I'm a Manchurian. Even after the Republic, it's still my country.

289
00:47:01,940 --> 00:47:06,610
那…秘密 皇上 又出来了
The... secret, Your Majesty, is emerging again.

290
00:47:23,920 --> 00:47:26,420
有什么事吗 皇上？
Is something the matter, Your Majesty?

291
00:47:27,420 --> 00:47:30,090
有事发生
-  Something is happening 

292
00:47:33,970 --> 00:47:36,010
发生了什么事 庄士敦先生？
What is happening, Mr.Johnston?

293
00:47:36,100 --> 00:47:38,180
- 没… - 住嘴!
- Nothing is... - Quiet.

294
00:48:21,810 --> 00:48:27,190
前来皇宫时 我们遭一群大学生所阻
on ourway here, Your Majesty, we were held up by students from the university.

295
00:48:28,230 --> 00:48:30,650
他们抗议民国政府
They were protesting against the Republican government...

296
00:48:30,740 --> 00:48:34,780
把国土割让给日本
because it has agreed to give away Chinese territory to Japan.

297
00:48:36,070 --> 00:48:38,240
庄士顿先生…
Is it true, Mr.Johnston...

298
00:48:38,330 --> 00:48:42,080
外面有许多人给砍头 这是真的么？
that many people out there have had their heads chopped off?

299
00:48:42,160 --> 00:48:44,960
是真的，皇上
It is true, Your Majesty.

300
00:48:45,040 --> 00:48:47,710
有许多人被砍头了
Many heads have been chopped off.

301
00:48:49,250 --> 00:48:52,090
使他们不再思考
It does stop them thinking.

302
00:48:52,170 --> 00:48:54,090
皇上该寝息了
It's time for the emperor's rest.

303
00:48:54,180 --> 00:48:57,090
学生愤怒是对的
The students are right to be angry.

304
00:49:02,350 --> 00:49:04,350
朕也愤怒!
I'm angry.

305
00:49:06,400 --> 00:49:09,150
但朕不获准离开紫禁城
But I'm not allowed to leave the Forbidden City.

306
00:49:11,030 --> 00:49:13,400
朕想到外面去
I want to go out, Mr.Johnston.

307
00:49:13,490 --> 00:49:16,160
陛下!
My lord.

308
00:49:16,240 --> 00:49:18,740
朕想看看繁闹城市!
I want to see the city of sounds.

309
00:49:27,540 --> 00:49:31,880
皇上赐你头品顶戴
The emperor awards you with the order of the Ruby Hat Button..

310
00:49:31,960 --> 00:49:36,590
赏坐四人肩舆
and with the right to be carried in your own chair with four bearers.

311
00:50:12,710 --> 00:50:16,970
此人走中道而我走侧道？
Ye'll take the high road and I'll take the low road?

312
00:51:25,910 --> 00:51:28,000
我希望皇上没有忘记
I hope the emperor has not forgotten...

313
00:51:28,080 --> 00:51:31,170
今天的数学课
that this is the day for his maths class.

314
00:51:38,840 --> 00:51:40,760
给皇上的！
For Your Majesty.

315
00:51:40,840 --> 00:51:43,800
太医说脚踏车不好
My doctor said bicycles are bad for you.

316
00:51:43,890 --> 00:51:46,140
对你有害？ 胡说！
Bad for you? Nonsense!

317
00:51:54,560 --> 00:51:56,570
怎么骑？
How does it work?

318
00:51:56,650 --> 00:51:58,610
噢
oh.

319
00:51:58,690 --> 00:52:01,360
很简单
It's simple.

320
00:52:01,450 --> 00:52:04,870
抬起头眼朝前看！
Head up and eyes forward.

321
00:52:06,160 --> 00:52:08,200
就象数学！
As in math.

322
00:52:32,140 --> 00:52:35,730
皇母死了 是吗? 是的 皇上
- My mother's dead, is she not? - Yes, Your Majesty.

323
00:52:36,860 --> 00:52:38,860
微臣替皇上难过
I'm profoundly sorry.

324
00:52:38,940 --> 00:52:40,940
朕不难过
I am not.

325
00:52:44,490 --> 00:52:48,200
她是自杀的 吞下鸦片球
She killed herself. She swallowed a ball of opium.

326
00:52:50,080 --> 00:52:53,160
朕去见她及皇弟
I'm going to see her and my brother.

327
00:54:23,880 --> 00:54:26,470
开门!
Open the door.

328
00:54:27,840 --> 00:54:29,840
开门!
open the door!

329
00:54:41,690 --> 00:54:43,690
开门!
Open the door.

330
00:55:31,450 --> 00:55:33,870
麻烦来了！
Trouble maker!

331
00:55:33,950 --> 00:55:37,870
魔头！管闲事的！
Devil! Meddler!

332
00:55:37,950 --> 00:55:40,500
麻烦 除了麻烦就是麻烦
Trouble. Nothing but trouble

333
00:55:40,580 --> 00:55:45,290
看你把我弄成何样子 你是个残忍无知的老头子
- Look where you lead him. - And you are an old, cruel, ignorant man!

334
00:55:45,380 --> 00:55:47,380
这孩子的母亲死了
The boy's mother is dead...

335
00:55:47,460 --> 00:55:49,380
竟不让他去看看！
and he's not even allowed to see her!

336
00:55:49,470 --> 00:55:51,380
朕要出去!
I want to go out!

337
00:55:51,470 --> 00:55:53,010
朕要出去!
I want to go out!

338
00:55:53,090 --> 00:55:54,850
别动！ 呆在那里别动！
Stop that! Stay where you are!

339
00:55:54,930 --> 00:55:57,720
- 朕要出去! - 别动！
- I want to go out! - Stop it!

340
00:55:57,810 --> 00:56:00,600
- 朕要出去! - 别动！呆在那里别动！笨蛋！
- I want to go out! - Stay where you are! You fool!

341
00:56:00,690 --> 00:56:02,100
别动！
Stay there!

342
00:56:03,310 --> 00:56:05,770
上！
Chang.

343
00:56:05,860 --> 00:56:07,860
驼背 大脚！
Hunchback. Big Foot.

344
00:56:35,850 --> 00:56:37,850
先生
Sir.

345
00:56:39,470 --> 00:56:47,820
把手伸给我 先生
Give me your hand, sir.

346
00:56:55,200 --> 00:56:57,160
你看不到吗？
Can you not see?

347
00:57:12,090 --> 00:57:14,630
请看我的左耳 先生
Look at my left ear, please, sir.

348
00:57:14,720 --> 00:57:18,600
谢谢 再看右耳
Thank you. And now my right.

349
00:57:18,680 --> 00:57:20,970
谢谢
Thank you

350
00:57:21,060 --> 00:57:23,020
请看着我的手指 先生
Would you follow my finger, please, sir?

351
00:57:29,400 --> 00:57:31,400
嗯嗯
Mm-hmm.

352
00:57:31,480 --> 00:57:35,240
非常简单 庄士敦 皇上需要眼镜
Well, it's perfectly simple, Johnston. The emperor needs spectacles.

353
00:57:35,320 --> 00:57:37,570
像莱特一样
Like Harold Lloyd.

354
00:57:37,660 --> 00:57:39,870
不可能
Impossible.

355
00:57:39,950 --> 00:57:41,830
皇上怎能戴眼镜
An emperor does not wear spectacles.

356
00:57:41,910 --> 00:57:44,830
这是不允许的!
That cannot be allowed

357
00:57:44,910 --> 00:57:48,130
时代不同了 殿下！
Times have changed, Your Highnesses.

358
00:58:03,350 --> 00:58:06,890
如果皇上不戴眼镜 庄士敦  他会失明的
If His Majesty doesn't get spectacles, Johnston, he could lose his sight.

359
00:58:11,520 --> 00:58:14,110
皇上
Your Majesty.

360
00:58:31,500 --> 00:58:35,760
如果皇上不戴眼镜  我就辞职
If the emperor does not get spectacles, I will resign.

361
00:58:35,840 --> 00:58:39,010
很不幸 决定不能改
Unfortunately, our decision is final.

362
00:58:39,090 --> 00:58:44,680
很不幸 我要说的将发表在中国的所有报纸上
And unfortunately, what I have to say will be published in every newspaper in China.

363
00:58:48,100 --> 00:58:50,690
您要说什么 庄士敦先生？
What do you have to say, Mr.Johnston?

364
00:58:52,570 --> 00:58:56,780
皇上在宫中有如囚犯 自登基直至逊位
The emperor has been a prisoner in his own palace since the day that he was crowned...

365
00:58:56,860 --> 00:58:59,110
皇上仍是个囚犯
and has remained a prisoner since he abdicated.

366
00:58:59,200 --> 00:59:01,370
皇上长大了会猜想何故
But now he's growing up, he may wonderwhy...

367
00:59:01,450 --> 00:59:05,950
自己是唯一不准出门的人
he is the only person in China who may not walk out of his own front door.

368
00:59:08,160 --> 00:59:11,540
我想皇上是世上最寂寞的孩子
I think the emperor is the loneliest boy on earth.

369
00:59:13,750 --> 00:59:16,380
同样悲惨是…
It would be conveniently sad..

370
00:59:16,460 --> 00:59:18,760
皇上失去视力
if he becomes blind

371
00:59:18,840 --> 00:59:21,090
失去视力…庄士敦先生?
Blind, Mr.Johnston?

372
00:59:22,470 --> 00:59:24,850
其代价 阁下
To the expense, Your Excellency.

373
00:59:24,930 --> 00:59:28,600
