Miss Windsor taught me how to do the dance ofthe quickstep.

436
01:08:26,560 --> 01:08:29,140
皇上知道怎样跳快步舞吗？
Does the emperor know how to do the quickstep?

437
01:08:30,560 --> 01:08:32,560
你会教我吗？
Will you teach me?

