- Good night. - Good night.

444
01:10:13,330 --> 01:10:15,620
你必须和我去牛津大学
You must come to Oxford with me.

445
01:10:21,750 --> 01:10:24,670
我喜欢他！
I like him.

446
01:10:24,760 --> 01:10:29,050
我肯定我会喜欢他！
I am sure I am going to like him.

447
01:10:29,140 --> 01:10:31,220
他会长大！
And he will grow up.

448
01:10:34,560 --> 01:10:36,560
朝下看！
Eyes down!

449
01:10:42,900 --> 01:10:45,070
先报告！
Report your arrival.

450
01:10:45,150 --> 01:10:47,780
- 981号犯人报告 - 大声点！
- Prisoner 981 reporting. - Louder!

451
01:10:47,860 --> 01:10:50,820
981号犯人报告
Prisoner 981 reporting.

452
01:10:50,910 --> 01:10:53,120
开门！
open the door.

453
01:10:58,750 --> 01:11:00,750
关门！
Close the door.

454
01:11:02,210 --> 01:11:04,800
坐下！
Sit down

455
01:11:09,180 --> 01:11:12,010
姓名！
Name.

456
01:11:12,100 --> 01:11:14,060
爱新觉罗・溥仪
Aisin-Gioro Pu Yi.

457
01:11:14,140 --> 01:11:16,140
写下来！
Write it.

458
01:11:35,740 --> 01:11:37,750
听着
Now then.

