or else he forgets to keep confessing.

463
01:11:53,930 --> 01:11:58,600
“水笼头”犯只需在他开始之前好好地拧一次
The water tap man needs one good, hard twist before he starts...

464
01:11:58,680 --> 01:12:01,350
接着什么都出来了
but then everything comes out.

465
01:12:01,440 --> 01:12:04,770
你是个聪明人
Now, you're an intelligent person

466
01:12:05,860 --> 01:12:07,980
我相信你明白我的话
I'm sure you understand me.

467
01:12:09,030 --> 01:12:10,950
好的
Good.

