那我们开始
Then we'll begin.

469
01:12:13,990 --> 01:12:16,580
你知道为什么你在这里吗 981？
Why do you think you're in here, 981?

470
01:12:16,660 --> 01:12:22,580
我被指控叛国、通敌和反革命
I am accused of being a traitor, a collaborator and a counter-revolutionary.

471
01:12:22,670 --> 01:12:25,420
那不是指控！ 你是一个叛国者
It is not an accusation! You are a traitor...

472
01:12:25,500 --> 01:12:29,090
你是一个通敌犯 并且你是一个反革命！
you are a collaborator, and you are a counter-revolutionary!

473
01:12:35,850 --> 01:12:38,560
你把这写下来了？
Did you write this?

474
01:12:38,640 --> 01:12:40,560
你称这是坦白？
And you call it a confession?

475
01:12:40,640 --> 01:12:44,600
这只是个时间表！一个童话！
This is nothing but a list of dates. A child's fairy tale.

476
01:12:56,160 --> 01:12:58,830
- 你们要我坦白什么？ -  你知道你做了什么
- What do you want me to confess? - You know what you did...

477
01:12:58,910 --> 01:13:00,830
别人做了什么
and what others did.

478
01:13:00,910 --> 01:13:03,120
为什么你不志愿提供消息呢？
So why don't you volunteer the information?

479
01:13:03,210 --> 01:13:04,870
我不明白
I do not understand.

480
01:13:04,960 --> 01:13:07,880
我们不告诉犯人坦白什么
We don't tell people what to confess.

481
01:13:07,960 --> 01:13:09,920
我们已经知道你全部的事情
We already know everything about you.

482
01:13:18,470 --> 01:13:20,970
我…
I...

483
01:13:22,180 --> 01:13:26,060
- 继续 - 我要改过自新
- Go on. - I wanted reforms.

484
01:13:26,150 --> 01:13:28,900
你要改什么过？
What did you want to reform?

485
01:13:28,980 --> 01:13:30,690
所有的事
Everything.

486
01:13:32,860 --> 01:13:34,820
剪掉辨子
Cut off my queue.

487
01:13:34,910 --> 01:13:37,410
皇上！不要！
Your Majesty. Please.

488
01:14:13,690 --> 01:14:17,490
- 它很重！- 以前的皇帝被谋杀
- It is heavy. - The emperor before me was murdered..

489
01:14:17,570 --> 01:14:20,620
是因为他们要改革帝国
because he wanted to reform the empire.

490
01:14:20,700 --> 01:14:22,620
是这样吗 庄士敦先生？
Is that not so, Mr.Johnston?

491
01:14:22,700 --> 01:14:25,710
是的 皇上 可能是
Yes, Your Majesty. Probably.

492
01:14:26,920 --> 01:14:31,750
我们看看他们是否杀朕 朕要改革紫禁城
Well, let us see if they will kill me for reforming the Forbidden City.

493
01:14:31,840 --> 01:14:34,260
总管
Lord Chamberlain

494
01:14:34,340 --> 01:14:39,260
朕在任命庄士敦先生的朋友 诗人和学者 陈小苏
I am appointing Mr.Johnston's friend, the poet and scholar Chen Hsiao Hsiu...

495
01:14:39,340 --> 01:14:41,800
来当新的内务总管
to be the new lord chamberlain.

496
01:14:41,890 --> 01:14:46,180
朕要他监督列个详细的库藏清单！
I want him to supervise a detailed inventory of the imperial storerooms...

497
01:14:46,270 --> 01:14:50,730
这样才会知道到底被偷了多少！
so that we can learn exactly how much has been stolen.

498
01:15:00,950 --> 01:15:05,700
紫禁城就象一个没有观众的剧院
The Forbidden City had become a theater without an audience

499
01:15:05,790 --> 01:15:09,290
为什么演员还要留在舞台上呢？
So why did the actors remain on the stage?

500
01:15:10,540 --> 01:15:14,420
仅仅是逐渐偷走布景
It was only to steal the scenery piece by piece.

501
01:15:28,440 --> 01:15:31,440
我能睡这里吗？ 我很害怕
Can I sleep here? I am frightened.

502
