你很勇敢
You're brave.

503
01:15:51,630 --> 01:15:53,630
你不害怕吗？
Are you not frightened?

504
01:15:54,800 --> 01:15:58,170
我很激动 我不想再逃避了
I am excited. I do not want to escape anymore.

505
01:15:59,590 --> 01:16:01,970
我要掌权
I want to rule.

506
01:16:04,600 --> 01:16:06,600
吻我
Kiss me.

507
01:16:38,050 --> 01:16:40,170
我也可以利你呆一起吗？
Can I stay with you as well?

508
01:16:42,180 --> 01:16:44,840
进来 进来
Get in. Get in.

509
