Your Majesty. The storerooms are on fire, Your Majesty.

517
01:19:40,100 --> 01:19:42,560
这是个巨大的损失
The fire was a terrible disaster..

518
01:19:42,650 --> 01:19:47,530
并且朕知道是太监们干的 就是要阻止朕查清谁偷了东西
and I knew the eunuchs had started it to stop me from knowing what they had stolen.

