01:22:21,510 --> 01:22:24,390
我们想知道关于日本的事
We want to know about the Japanese.

530
01:22:26,100 --> 01:22:28,480
你和日本人的关系是怎么开始的？
How did your friendship with the Japanese begin?

531
01:22:28,560 --> 01:22:30,020
谁介绍的？！什么时候？！
Who introduced you? When?

532
01:22:33,150 --> 01:22:35,490
