01:24:52,500 --> 01:24:54,750
你们总得离开紫禁城
You always wanted to leave the Forbidden City.

553
01:24:54,830 --> 01:24:57,840
你们只有一小时时间收拾 所以快去！
Now you've got an hour to pack. So go!

554
01:24:59,170 --> 01:25:00,840
快啊！
Go!

555
01:25:13,310 --> 01:25:16,060
我总以为我恨这里
I always thought I hated it here.

556
01:25:17,190 --> 01:25:19,570
现在我害怕离开
Now I'm afraid to leave

557
01:25:19,650 --> 01:25:22,820
- 你认为他们会杀我吗？ - 按他们说的做 皇上
- Do you think they will kill me? - You must do as they say, Your Majesty...

558
01:25:22,900 --> 01:25:25,530
我将去英国大使馆
while I try to reach the British Embassy

559
01:25:25,620 --> 01:25:27,950
他们会给你庇护权
They will give you asylum there

560
01:25:29,040 --> 01:25:31,660
我肯定他们会的
I'm sure they will.

561
01:25:31,750 --> 01:25:36,210
张 把我的车开到南门！ 我要送皇上
Chang, take my car to the south gate. I want you to drive His Majesty.

562
01:26:36,730 --> 01:26:38,980
皇上！
Your Majesty!

563
01:27:26,530 --> 01:27:28,780
- 请 皇上！ - 什么？
- Please, Your Majesty. - What?

564
01:28:16,330 --> 01:28:19,870
但你没有去英国使馆 是不是？
But you didn't go to the British Embassy, did you?

565
01:28:19,960 --> 01:28:22,040
你反而去了日本使馆
You ended up at the Japanese Embassy.

566
01:28:22,130 --> 01:28:25,040
日本人是唯一准备帮助我的人
The Japanese were the only people prepared to help me.

567
01:28:25,130 --> 01:28:27,130
他们白帮你？
Help you for nothing?

568
01:28:28,840 --> 01:28:32,760
日本有个皇帝 我们年龄差不多
Japan has an emperor. We are almost the same age.

569
01:28:32,840 --> 01:28:35,970
我想是出于善意
I thought it was kindness.

570
01:28:36,060 --> 01:28:40,520
同时我意识到很多中国人 认为我是异族人
At the same time I realized that, for many Chinese, I was an alien...

571
01:28:40,600 --> 01:28:43,850
只是因为我是满洲人
simply because I am Manchurian.

572
01:28:43,940 --> 01:28:49,150
甚至有个反满同盟要暗杀我！
There was even an anti-Manchurian league who wanted to assassinate me.

573
01:28:49,240 --> 01:28:52,240
所以 我想住在天津
So I went to live in Tientsin.

574
01:28:53,870 --> 01:28:58,830
那是有个大港口的好地方
It was a nice, provincial town with a big port.

575
01:28:58,910 --> 01:29:02,580
那些日子  我们做了重大的决定
In those days they had a large international settlement

576
01:29:02,670 --> 01:29:05,460
日本人认为我在那里会安全些
The Japanese thought it would be safer for me there

577
01:29:05,540 --> 01:29:08,300
在天津日本人替你付钱吗？
were the Japanese paying for you in Tientsin?

578
01:29:08,380 --> 01:29:10,300
噢 不是
oh, no.

579
01:29:10,380 --> 01:29:13,720
我只好租一栋公馆 张公馆  
I had to rent a villa - the Villa Chang.

580
01:29:13,800 --> 01:29:16,010
非常昂贵
And it was very expensive.

581
01:29:16,100 --> 01:29:18,260
保镖也是
So were the bodyguards.

582
01:29:19,270 --> 01:29:21,770
我在天津花了很多钱
I spent a lot of money in Tientsin

583
01:29:21,850 --> 01:29:25,940
你那时还想恢复大清帝国吗？
Did you still believe in a restoration of the imperial system?

584
01:29:26,020 --> 01:29:29,190
其他人想 后来被抓并流放了
others did. The little court in exile

585
01:29:30,690 --> 01:29:34,280
我记不清他们让我花费了多少 翡翠珠宝
I cannot remember how much jade and jewelry they made me spend...

586
01:29:34,360 --> 01:29:39,330
来讨好一些军阀利一些俄国将军
to buy the friendship of some warlord or some White Russian general.

587
01:29:39,410 --> 01:29:41,240
你的钱还花在哪儿了？
What else did you spend your money on?

588
01:29:41,330 --> 01:29:46,040
我是不厌其烦地买钢琴  手表 收音机…
I was never tired of buying pianos, watches, radios.

589
01:29:46,130 --> 01:29:48,420
只要是外国造的都买！
As long as they were foreign

590
01:29:48,500 --> 01:29:50,420
当然
of course.

591
01:29:50,510 --> 01:29:52,630
西方的任何东西都好
Anything western was good.

592
01:29:52,720 --> 01:29:56,930
特别是WrigLey口香糖  Bayer阿斯匹林和汽车
Especially Wrigley's Chewing Gum, Bayer Aspirin, and cars.

593
01:29:57,010 --> 01:29:59,350
你在天津时…
While you were in Tientsin...

594
01:29:59,430 --> 01:30:03,230
中国大部分土地由蒋介石统治
most of China came under the control of General Chiang Kai-shek...

595
01:30:03,310 --> 01:30:05,560
号称民族主义的
the so-called nationalists...

596
01:30:05,650 --> 01:30:07,730
国民党
the Kuomintang.

597
01:30:07,810 --> 01:30:10,980
- 你利他们是什么关系？- 没有
- What were your relations with them? - None.

598
01:30:13,150 --> 01:30:16,360
我觉得留在天津毫无意义
I felt useless in Tientsin.

599
01:30:16,450 --> 01:30:19,070
我都21岁了
I was 21 .

600
01:30:19,160 --> 01:30:22,410
我梦想去西方
I dreamt of going to the west.

601
01:30:22,500 --> 01:30:24,410
我变成了花花公子
I became a playboy.

602
01:30:24,500 --> 01:30:28,670
我忧郁
# Am I blue #

603
01:30:28,750 --> 01:30:31,750
我沮丧
# Am I blue #

604
01:30:31,840 --> 01:30:34,970
我眼中的泪水会
# Ain't these tears in my eyes #

605
01:30:35,050 --> 01:30:38,720
告诉你
# Telling you # 

606
01:30:38,800 --> 01:30:41,140
我忧郁
# Am I blue #

607
01:30:41,220 --> 01:30:44,140
你也会这样
# You'd be too #

608
01:30:44,230 --> 01:30:47,310
如果你和女友
# If each plan with your girl #

609
01:30:47,400 --> 01:30:50,190
分手了
# Done fell through #

610
01:30:51,270 --> 01:30:53,480
曾经
# Was a time #

611
01:30:53,570 --> 01:30:57,530
我是她的唯一
# I was her only one #

612
01:30:57,610 --> 01:30:59,780
但是现在
# But now #

613
01:30:59,870 --> 01:31:05,160
我又悲伤又孤独
# I'm the sad and lonely one #

614
01:31:10,840 --> 01:31:14,710
现在她走了 我们也结束了
# Now she's gone and we're through #

615
01:31:14,800 --> 01:31:19,470
上帝啊 我忧郁
# Lord, I'm blue 

616
01:31:19,550 --> 01:31:21,550
太棒了！
Very good!

617
01:31:31,230 --> 01:31:33,230
很好！
well done!

618
01:32:08,850 --> 01:32:11,440
那船很棒 如果您坐头等舱
That's a great ship if you're going first class.

619
01:32:14,730 --> 01:32:16,900
我哪里也不去
I am not going anywhere.

620
01:32:20,530 --> 01:32:22,410
想跳舞吗？
Would you like to dance?

621
01:32:32,210 --> 01:32:35,920
你很勇敢  这里没人敢和我跳舞
You are a brave man. Nobody here would have danced with me.

622
01:32:36,000 --> 01:32:38,840
为什么？
Why is that?

623
01:32:38,920 --> 01:32:40,670
因为我是中国人
Because I'm Chinese.

624
01:32:40,760 --> 01:32:43,090
我是美国人
Well, I'm American.

625
01:32:53,900 --> 01:32:57,150
你说加利福尼亚 我说法国里维埃拉
You say California. I say French Riviera.

626
01:32:57,230 --> 01:32:59,070
说弗朗西斯科（旧金山）！
San Francisco!

627
01:32:59,150 --> 01:33:01,570
蒙特卡洛！
Monte Carlo!

628
01:33:01,650 --> 01:33:04,160
这次我们真的走吗？
Are we really going this time?

629
01:33:13,420 --> 01:33:15,330
那一对是谁？
Who's that couple?

630
01:33:15,420 --> 01:33:18,340
是亨利和伊丽莎白
Oh. Henry and Elizabeth.

631
01:33:18,420 --> 01:33:20,340
中国的皇帝？
The emperor of China?

632
01:33:20,420 --> 01:33:22,760
以前的皇帝和他的妻子
The ex-emperor and his wife.

633
01:33:24,590 --> 01:33:27,850
- 她很漂亮 - 是的 非常
- She's beautiful. - Yes, very.

634
01:33:27,930 --> 01:33:29,850
那你是谁？
And who are you?

635
01:33:29,930 --> 01:33:33,270
- 我是殿下的另一个妻子 -他的另一个妻子？
- I am His Highness's other wife. - His otherwife?

636
01:33:33,350 --> 01:33:35,900
二号妻子
Number two wife.

637
01:33:35,980 --> 01:33:38,190
是吗 有些人真是幸运
Well, some people have all the luck.

638
01:33:54,170 --> 01:33:56,080
女士们先生们！
Ladies and gentlemen!

639
01:33:59,340 --> 01:34:01,880
蒋介石将军
General Chiang Kai-shek...

640
01:34:01,960 --> 01:34:04,380
已经占领了上海
has taken Shanghai.

641
01:34:04,470 --> 01:34:07,390
国民党已与共产党决裂
The Kuomintang have broken with the Reds...

642
01:34:07,470 --> 01:34:09,390
并6次击败了他们！
and have knocked them for six!

643
01:34:09,470 --> 01:34:12,390
-共产党完了！
- The Reds are finished! 

644
01:34:17,900 --> 01:34:21,320
对此次接见的每一个人表示歉意
Sorry about the reception, everyone. We'll get it fixed in a minute.

645
01:34:21,400 --> 01:34:24,900
现在最好返回日本领事馆 皇上
It would be wiser to return to the Japanese Legation now, Your Majesty.

646
01:34:24,990 --> 01:34:29,120
- 您的车准备好了 - 谢谢你 甘糟先生
- Your car is waiting. -Thank you, Mr. Amakasu.

647
01:34:29,200 --> 01:34:31,200
出发吧
Here we go.

648
01:34:41,840 --> 01:34:46,170
上海的总罢工已经失败了
The general strike in Shanghai has collapsed

649
01:34:46,260 --> 01:34:50,010
国际租借很安全的
The international settlement is safe

650
01:34:50,100 --> 01:34:52,010
国民党军队…
Troops of the Kuomintang..

651
01:34:52,100 --> 01:34:54,560
完全控制了这个城市
are now in full control ofthe city...

652
01:34:54,640 --> 01:34:59,730
正用有力的措施恢复平民区的秩序
and firm steps are being taken to restore order in the native areas

653
01:35:09,490 --> 01:35:12,490
文绣 要口香糖吗？
Wen Hsiu, you want some gum?

654
01:35:16,290 --> 01:35:18,290
我要离婚
I want a divorce.

655
01:35:24,630 --> 01:35:27,170
我再也不想当你的情妇了
I do not want to be your mistress any longer.

656
01:35:27,260 --> 01:35:30,180
我认为你是我的贵妃
I thought you were my secondary consort.

657
01:35:30,260 --> 01:35:34,680
在紫禁城 你是皇帝我是贵妃
In the Forbidden City, you were the emperor and I was your secondary consort.

658
01:35:35,810 --> 01:35:38,690
但现在你是亨利溥仪
But now you are Henry Pu Yi.

659
01:35:38,770 --> 01:35:41,600
婉容是你的妻子 伊丽莎白
Wan Yung is your wife, Elizabeth.

660
01:35:43,400 --> 01:35:45,570
那我算什么？
And who am I?

661
01:35:46,860 --> 01:35:49,610
我什么都不是
I'm nobody. 

662
01:35:58,500 --> 01:36:01,670
我不知道你这么不高兴
I did not know you were so unhappy.

663
01:36:06,170 --> 01:36:09,170
在西方你只能娶一个妻子
You can only have one wife in the West.

664
01:36:14,810 --> 01:36:16,720
我要离婚
I want a divorce.

665
01:36:16,810 --> 01:36:18,810
没人能和我离婚！
No one can divorce me.

666
01:36:43,130 --> 01:36:45,380
我要离婚！
I want a divorce!

667
01:37:20,750 --> 01:37:25,880
夫人！
Your Ladyship!

668
01:37:32,340 --> 01:37:34,340
谢谢
Thank you.

669
01:37:48,650 --> 01:37:50,650
我不需要！
I do not need it!

670
01:37:54,820 --> 01:37:56,820
我不需要！
I do not need it.

671
01:38:26,230 --> 01:38:28,150
文绣
Wen Hsiu. 

672
01:38:39,370 --> 01:38:42,200
伊丽莎白！我可以进来吗？
Elizabeth, can I come in?

673
01:38:42,290 --> 01:38:44,580
不记得我了？我穿得象个飞行员
Don't you remember me?

674
01:38:44,660 --> 01:38:47,710
我穿得象个飞行员 但我还不能飞！还不能
I'm dressed like a pilot, but I still can't fly. Not yet.

675
01:38:47,790 --> 01:38:51,210
东方明珠！ 我们一起上舞蹈课！
Eastern Jewel! We had dancing classes together.

676
01:38:51,300 --> 01:38:53,460
是的 恰在你结婚前
Yes, just before your marriage.

677
01:38:53,550 --> 01:38:57,180
傻女孩 为什么人想要结婚呢？
You silly girl. Why do people want to get married?

678
01:38:57,260 --> 01:38:59,840
文绣走了
Wen Hsiu has gone.

679
01:38:59,930 --> 01:39:01,850
她再也不会回来了
She will never come back.

680
01:39:01,930 --> 01:39:03,930
那很糟糕吗？
Is that so bad?

681
01:39:05,100 --> 01:39:07,270
她是我唯一的朋友
She was my only friend.

682
01:39:08,440 --> 01:39:12,110
是的  但至少你可以独享你的丈夫了！
Well, at least now you've got your husband all to yourself.

683
01:39:13,780 --> 01:39:15,780
你有了我！
And you've got me!

684
01:39:17,200 --> 01:39:19,450
我会做你的朋友
I'll be your friend.

685
01:39:19,530 --> 01:39:21,620
- 你吸鸦片？ - 可恶
- You smoke opium? - Be wicked.

686
01:39:21,700 --> 01:39:23,700
这是上海最好的东西
It's the best in Shanghai.

687
01:39:25,290 --> 01:39:27,290
什么你要去欧洲？
Why are you going to Europe?

688
01:39:27,370 --> 01:39:30,790
应该去日本！ 哪儿比任何地方都有趣！
The place to go is Japan. It's more fun than anywhere.

689
01:39:32,130 --> 01:39:34,880
时髦的地方
It's modern

690
01:39:34,960 --> 01:39:38,760
你怎么知道我们要去欧洲？ 这是个秘密
How do you know we are going to Europe? It is a secret.

691
01:39:38,840 --> 01:39:41,050
我知道所有的事！
Oh, I know everything.

692
01:39:41,140 --> 01:39:45,220
我知道蒋介石有假牙
I know Chiang Kai-shek has got false teeth.

693
01:39:45,310 --> 01:39:48,310
我甚至知道他的绰号 “给我换现金！”
I even know his nickname..."Cash My Check!"

694
01:39:52,190 --> 01:39:54,820
我是间谍…
I'm a spy...

695
01:39:54,900 --> 01:39:57,110
我不怕别人知道
and I don't care who knows it.

696
01:39:57,190 --> 01:40:00,860
- 间谍？ - 我为日本特别行动部工作
- A spy? - I work for the Japanese Special Service Bureau.

697
01:40:00,950 --> 01:40:03,450
我是来保护你的
And I've come to protect you.

698
01:40:04,450 --> 01:40:07,000
日本人…
The Japanese...

699
01:40:07,080 --> 01:40:10,160
他们越来越接近他
They are getting closer to him every day.

700
01:40:11,250 --> 01:40:15,630
他正想送他弟弟去东京的军事学院
He is sending his brother to the military academy in Tokyo.

701
01:40:15,710 --> 01:40:18,920
他们一直利他谈论满洲的事
They talk to him about Manchuria all the time.

702
01:40:20,050 --> 01:40:22,970
甘糟先生不再和我打招呼
And Mr. Amakasu never says hello to me.

703
01:40:23,050 --> 01:40:24,970
我不信任日本人
I do not trust the Japanese.

704
01:40:36,690 --> 01:40:39,610
当然 我很想当皇帝的第二夫人！
Of course, I'd love to be the emperor's new secondary consort.

705
01:40:39,700 --> 01:40:43,320
- 东方明珠 - 如果那位子能够得到
- Eastern Jewel. - If the post is available.

706
01:41:01,840 --> 01:41:04,840
那位子是空着 亲爱的表妹
The post is vacant, my dear cousin.

707
01:41:06,640 --> 01:41:09,140
但你不适合那位子
But you do not fit the part.

708
01:41:11,890 --> 01:41:14,810
文绣把狗拉下了 你想要吗？
Wen Hsiu left the dog behind. Do you want it?

709
01:41:16,900 --> 01:41:19,230
是我的错
It is my fault.

710
01:41:19,320 --> 01:41:21,570
都是我的错
It is all my fault.

711
01:41:53,980 --> 01:41:56,480
我来看看您 皇上
I came to see you, Your Majesty...

712
01:41:56,560 --> 01:41:58,560
给您带来了坏消息
to give you bad news.

713
01:41:59,860 --> 01:42:02,030
一些可怕的事发生了
Something terrible has happened

714
01:42:07,870 --> 01:42:10,790
我们满洲先皇的陵墓
The imperial tombs of our Manchurian ancestors...

715
01:42:10,870 --> 01:42:13,580
被盗掘了
have been attacked and robbed...

716
01:42:13,660 --> 01:42:16,790
是国民党军队干的
by troops of the Kuomintang

717
01:42:16,880 --> 01:42:19,250
是中国士兵
Chinese soldiers

718
01:42:19,340 --> 01:42:21,500
一个蒋介石手下的军阀
A warlord working for Chiang Kai-shek

719
01:42:25,340 --> 01:42:28,760
慈禧太后的遗体
The body of the Empress Dowager...

720
01:42:28,850 --> 01:42:30,850
被劈成了碎片
was hacked to pieces.

721
01:42:32,850 --> 01:42:37,150
她的珍珠项链成了蒋介石的一个结婚礼物
Her pearl necklace has become a wedding present from Chiang Kai-shek...

722
01:42:37,230 --> 01:42:39,230
给他新妻子的
to his new wife.

723
01:43:01,000 --> 01:43:03,800
告诉我 981号 你想不想成为一个中国人？
Tell me, 981 , do you consider yourself to be Chinese?

724
01:43:03,880 --> 01:43:05,800
当然想
of course.

725
01:43:05,880 --> 01:43:07,800
- 这是什么？ - 日本
- What is this? -Japan.

726
01:43:07,890 --> 01:43:10,680
- 你把中国的这个部分叫什么？ - 东北
- And what do you call this part ofChina? - The northeast.

727
01:43:10,760 --> 01:43:14,020
- 你小时候把它叫什么？- 满洲
- And what did you call it as a child? - Manchuria.

728
01:43:14,100 --> 01:43:18,140
日本在1931年9月18日入侵了满洲
Japan invaded Manchuria on September 18, 1931 ...

729
01:43:18,230 --> 01:43:21,150
并开始建立一个叫满洲国的傀儡国家
and began to set up a puppet state called Manchukuo.

730
01:43:21,230 --> 01:43:25,440
之后不久 一个日本代表团在天津对你进行了一次秘密拜访
Shortly afterwards, a Japanese delegation paid you a secret visit in Tientsin...

731
01:43:25,530 --> 01:43:27,450
请求你的合作
to request your collaboration.

732
01:43:27,530 --> 01:43:29,450
你拒绝了吗？
Would you say you refused?

733
01:43:29,530 --> 01:43:32,030
- 大声说！ - 我已经告诉了你们
- Speak up! - I already told you.

734
01:43:32,120 --> 01:43:35,370
- 我对你们说了一百遍了 - 再说一遍！跟我们说200遍！
- I have told you a hundred times. - Tell us again. Tell us 200 times.

735
01:43:35,450 --> 01:43:37,370
我拒绝合作
I refused to collaborate.

736
01:43:37,460 --> 01:43:39,370
你说你拒绝了
You say you refused.

737
01:43:39,460 --> 01:43:44,750
但一个月后 在1931年11月10日 你到了满洲
But a month later, on November 10, 1931 , there you are arriving in Manchuria.

738
01:43:44,840 --> 01:43:47,050
或许我应该称它为满洲国？
or should I call it Manchukuo?

739
01:43:47,130 --> 01:43:50,550
根据你的这份所谓的供词
Now, according to this so-called confession of yours...

740
01:43:50,640 --> 01:43:52,550
你并不是自愿走的
you didn't go of your own free will.

741
01:43:52,640 --> 01:43:54,970
你坚持说 你是被日本人绑架去的！
You insist that you were kidnapped by theJapanese!

742
01:43:55,060 --> 01:43:57,100
- 是的 - 是被强迫带到满洲的
- Yes. - And taken to Manchuria by force

743
01:43:57,180 --> 01:43:59,770
- 是的！ - 坐下
- Yes! - Sit down.

744
01:44:02,860 --> 01:44:06,940
你记不记得一个叫雷金纳德.弗莱明.庄士敦的人？
Do you remember a man called Reginald Fleming Johnston?

745
01:44:08,280 --> 01:44:10,700
他是你的私人教师
He was your tutor.

746
01:44:10,780 --> 01:44:12,700
是的
Yes.

747
01:44:12,780 --> 01:44:15,280
还是好朋友 我想
And a good friend, I believe.

748
01:44:17,160 --> 01:44:19,870
在中国待了28年后
After 28 years in China...

749
01:44:19,960 --> 01:44:22,920
庄士敦回到了英格兰
Mr.Johnston returned to England.

750
01:44:23,000 --> 01:44:27,800
他成了伦敦大学的一个东方文化的教授
He became a professor of Oriental Studies at London University...

751
01:44:28,840 --> 01:44:31,180
他写了一本书
and he wrote a book

752
01:44:31,260 --> 01:44:34,350
书名是《紫禁城的黄昏》
It is called Twilight in the Forbidden City...

753
01:44:34,430 --> 01:44:36,930
它是献给你的
and it is dedicated to you.

754
01:44:52,610 --> 01:44:54,530
再见！
Bye now!

755
01:44:54,620 --> 01:44:56,530
- 再见！ - 再见了！
- Bye! - Good-bye!

756
01:44:56,620 --> 01:44:59,370
- 别忘了写信 - 再见噢！
- Don't forget to write! - Bye, Mom!

757
01:45:04,630 --> 01:45:07,750
我会想念你的 庄士顿
I am going to miss you, Johnston.

758
01:45:07,840 --> 01:45:10,760
我也会想念你 皇上
I shall miss you, Your Majesty.

759
01:45:14,180 --> 01:45:18,470
你认为一个人可以再次成为皇帝么？
Do you think a man can become emperor again?

760
01:45:18,560 --> 01:45:20,100
是的
Yes.

761
01:45:38,910 --> 01:45:41,120
谢谢您 皇上
Thank you, Your Majesty.

762
01:45:43,080 --> 01:45:46,960
全部上船！全部上船！全部上船！
All aboard! All aboard! All aboard!

763
01:45:47,040 --> 01:45:49,050
我们怎能说“再见”？
How can we say good-bye?

764
01:45:50,760 --> 01:45:52,760
就象我们说“您好”
As we said hello.

765
01:46:05,150 --> 01:46:07,400
再见 庄士敦先生
Farewell, Mr.Johnston.

766
01:46:07,480 --> 01:46:09,480
再见 皇上！
Farewell, Your Majesty.

767
01:46:15,450 --> 01:46:19,620
全部上船！全部上船！
All aboard! All aboard!

768
01:46:19,700 --> 01:46:21,620
谢谢你
Thank you.

769
01:46:21,700 --> 01:46:23,700
谢谢你
Thank you

770
01:46:24,920 --> 01:46:26,830
全部上船！全部上船！
- All aboard! - All aboard!

771
01:46:30,800 --> 01:46:32,800
现在全部上船！
All aboard now!

772
01:46:34,590 --> 01:46:37,340
全部上船！
All aboard!

773
01:46:43,520 --> 01:46:47,060
全部上船！
All aboard!

774
01:46:56,740 --> 01:46:58,820
再见 庄士顿先生！
Good-bye, Mr.Johnston!

775
01:46:58,910 --> 01:47:01,990
我们永远不会忘记你 庄士敦先生
We'll never forget you, Mr.Johnston!

776
01:47:02,080 --> 01:47:05,750
再见！庄士敦先生 再见！再见！
Good-bye! Mr.Johnston, good-bye!

777
01:47:05,830 --> 01:47:08,290
- 再见！ - 全部上船！
- Good-bye! - All aboard!

778
01:47:11,130 --> 01:47:15,800
在第449页…
On page 449...

779
01:47:15,880 --> 01:47:17,800
庄士敦先生写到
Mr.Johnston writes:

780
01:47:17,880 --> 01:47:23,470
声称皇帝是被日本人绑架一事
"The endeavor to make out that the emperor had been kidnapped by the Japanese...

781
01:47:23,560 --> 01:47:25,810
完全是不真实的
"is wholly untrue.

782
01:47:27,190 --> 01:47:29,770
他离开天津去满洲…
"He left Tientsin and went to Manchuria...

783
01:47:29,860 --> 01:47:31,770
是他完全自愿的
of his own free will."

784
01:47:31,860 --> 01:47:34,690
- 庄士敦在说谎！- 你说什么？
-Johnston was a liar. - what did you say?

785
01:47:34,780 --> 01:47:39,030
庄士敦先生在我被带去满洲前就已离开了
Mr.Johnston had left before I was taken to Manchuria.

786
01:47:39,110 --> 01:47:41,490
他不知道都发生了什么事情
He could not have known what happened.

787
01:47:58,260 --> 01:48:00,260
坐下
Sit down.

788
01:48:07,180 --> 01:48:11,770
根据这份供词 你在11月9日的早晨把这个人的行李打点好的
According to this account, you prepared the man's things on the morning of November 9.

789
01:48:11,860 --> 01:48:14,020
对一个被绑架的人来说
Isn't it unusual for a man who is kidnapped...

790
01:48:14,110 --> 01:48:17,230
在他被绑架的前一天让仆人准备好行李 这正常吗？
to have his luggage packed by his valet the day before he is kidnapped?

791
01:48:17,320 --> 01:48:21,070
这是你写的 是不是？ 是谁让你去准备这个人的行李的？
This is what you have written, isn't it? Who told you to pack this man's luggage?

792
01:48:24,660 --> 01:48:27,290
这两个故事不相符 不是吗？
These two stories don't fit, do they?

793
01:48:29,330 --> 01:48:32,000
时间太久了
It was a long time ago.

794
01:48:32,080 --> 01:48:34,170
大概我弄错了
Perhaps I made a mistake.

795
01:48:34,250 --> 01:48:37,130
你在说谎！你们都在说谎！
You are lying! You are both lying!

796
01:48:38,010 --> 01:48:40,010
冷静点！
Control yourself!

797
01:48:46,350 --> 01:48:48,520
你仍然可以改变你的看法
You can still change your mind.

798
01:48:53,730 --> 01:48:58,730
我是满洲人民的世袭统治者
I am the hereditary ruler of the Manchurian people.

799
01:49:00,650 --> 01:49:05,030
没有我就没有满洲国
There can be no Manchukuo without me.

800
01:49:05,120 --> 01:49:08,620
你没看出来？日本人在利用你
Do you not see? The Japanese are using you.

801
01:49:09,620 --> 01:49:12,370
我必须试着利用他们
I must try to use them.

802
01:49:12,460 --> 01:49:16,340
日本对满洲的侵略将被国际联盟所谴责
The Japanese invasion of Manchuria will be condemned by the League of Nations...

803
01:49:16,420 --> 01:49:18,590
包括地球上所有的文明国家
and by every civilized country on Earth.

804
01:49:18,670 --> 01:49:22,170
民国违背了它对我许下的每一个诺言！
The Chinese Republic has broken every promise it ever made to me.

805
01:49:22,260 --> 01:49:25,840
中国军队侮辱了我先祖的陵墓！
Chinese troops desecrated the tombs of my ancestors.

806
01:49:25,930 --> 01:49:29,140
并且中国军队没有在日本进攻时保卫满洲！
And Chinese troops did not defend Manchuria from the Japanese.

807
01:49:29,220 --> 01:49:31,980
但满洲仍是中国！
But Manchuria is still China!

808
01:49:32,060 --> 01:49:35,730
- 中国已经抛弃了我 - 请不要走
- China has turned its back on me. - Please, do not go.

809
01:49:35,810 --> 01:49:39,150
满洲是最富饶的亚洲边疆！
Manchuria is the richest frontier in Asia.

810
01:49:39,230 --> 01:49:41,860
煤 油 铁路！
Coal, oil, railways!

811
01:49:41,950 --> 01:49:44,910
每年都有上百万的中国移民去那里！
Millions of Chinese immigrants are going there every year.

812
01:49:44,990 --> 01:49:46,910
我将建立我的国家
I'm going to build my country.

813
01:49:46,990 --> 01:49:50,410
庄士敦错了 但他不是个说谎者
Johnston was wrong, but he wasn't a liar.

814
01:49:50,500 --> 01:49:52,960
不存在绑架！
There was no kidnapping.

815
01:49:53,040 --> 01:49:57,960
去满洲是你自己的选择 是因为你想再次成为皇帝！
You went to Manchuria by your own choice because you wanted to be emperor again!

816
01:50:14,060 --> 01:50:17,060
这些东西或许能帮助你回忆真相
These might help you to remember the truth.

817
01:51:55,870 --> 01:51:57,870
对天
To heaven.

818
01:52:04,380 --> 01:52:07,300
对地
To earth.

819
01:52:07,380 --> 01:52:09,470
对月
To the moon

820
01:52:12,350 --> 01:52:14,810
对日
To the sun.

821
01:52:31,490 --> 01:52:33,490
你又是皇后了
You're an empress again.

822
01:52:34,990 --> 01:52:37,490
我想做的是飞行员！
What I'm going to be is a pilot.

823
01:52:37,580 --> 01:52:41,750
我将在横滨附近的一个秘密基地训练学习精确轰炸
I'm going to train at a secret base near Yokohama to learn precision bombing.

824
01:52:43,040 --> 01:52:45,460
我想轰炸上海
I want to bomb Shanghai.

825
01:52:46,710 --> 01:52:48,960
轰炸上海？
Bomb Shanghai?

826
01:52:49,050 --> 01:52:51,050
我恨中国！
I hate China.

827
01:52:57,140 --> 01:52:59,140
我恨你
I hate you.

828
01:54:18,560 --> 01:54:22,890
日本军最高统帅部！ 印象深刻！
The Japanese army high command. Very impressive!

829
01:54:24,020 --> 01:54:26,770
日本军队！
The Japanese army!

830
01:54:35,240 --> 01:54:37,240
快！
Quickly!

831
01:54:55,680 --> 01:54:58,090
代表日本天皇
On behalf of the emperor of Japan...

832
01:54:58,180 --> 01:55:03,220
关东军司令官表达他最热烈的祝贺
the commander of the Kwangtung Army extends his warmest congratulations...

833
01:55:03,310 --> 01:55:06,810
在皇帝的加冕仪式上
on the occasion of His Majesty's coronation

834
01:55:49,020 --> 01:55:50,940
呵 是的
Ah, yes.

835
01:55:54,780 --> 01:55:57,690
满洲国将成为一个伟大的国家
Manchukuo will grow into a great nation

836
01:55:57,780 --> 01:56:01,110
日本将一直站在皇帝一边
Japan will always be at her side to help her.

837
01:57:02,390 --> 01:57:05,100
我给你介绍一下？
Uh, may I introduce you?

838
01:57:05,180 --> 01:57:08,470
- 我妻子 广岛公主
- My wife, the Princess Hiro Saga.

839
01:57:08,560 --> 01:57:10,770
总理大臣郑孝胥
Prime Minister Hsiao Hsiu

840
01:57:15,770 --> 01:57:18,900
尊敬的国防大臣张景惠
The Honorable Chang Chinghui Minister of Defense.

841
01:57:20,990 --> 01:57:24,160
教廷特使 科隆阁下
The Papal Nuncio, Monsignor Colonna.

842
01:57:38,590 --> 01:57:42,300
朕和皇后非常高兴地接受…
The empress and I accept with great pleasure...

843
01:57:49,310 --> 01:57:51,390
对不起 将军
Excuse me, General.

844
01:58:14,290 --> 01:58:17,540
还有我们的甘粕先生
Ah, and our Mr. Amakasu...

845
01:58:17,630 --> 01:58:21,800
他是满洲电影会的新主席
is the new chief of the Manchurian Motion Picture Studios.

846
01:58:31,140 --> 01:58:34,520
为什么你不好好享受呢？
Why do you have to spoil this day?

847
01:58:34,600 --> 01:58:36,600
为什么？
Why?

848
01:58:38,150 --> 01:58:43,110
甘粕先生是满洲国最有权势的人
Mr. Amakasu is the most powerful man in Manchukuo.

849
01:58:43,190 --> 01:58:45,450
你在说什么？
What are you talking about?

850
01:58:46,490 --> 01:58:50,870
你不相信我能再当皇帝 但我是了
You did not believe I could be emperor again, but I am.

851
01:58:50,950 --> 01:58:52,950
你糊涂
You are blind.

852
01:59:02,670 --> 01:59:06,590
你知道当皇后意味着什么吗？ 你是皇后！
Do you know what it means to be an empress? You are an empress.

853
01:59:10,760 --> 01:59:12,930
为什么你不再和我做爱？
Why do you not make love to me anymore?

854
01:59:13,020 --> 01:59:14,980
因为你已经成了鸦片鬼
Because you have become an opium addict.

855
01:59:16,730 --> 01:59:20,020
鸦片杀了我母亲  鸦片毁了中国
Opium killed my mother. Opium destroyed China.

856
01:59:20,110 --> 01:59:22,650
你可在满洲国任何地方买到鸦片！
You can buy opium anywhere in Manchukuo.

857
01:59:22,730 --> 01:59:24,650
- 住口！ - 在任一个商店
- Shut up. - In any shop.

858
01:59:24,740 --> 01:59:27,030
住口！
Shut up!

859
01:59:29,450 --> 01:59:31,910
你弟弟要生小孩了
Your brother is going to have a child.

860
01:59:34,500 --> 01:59:36,500
我们必须有个孩子
we must have a child

861
01:59:37,670 --> 01:59:40,250
我们必须有个继承人
You must have an heir.

862
01:59:41,670 --> 01:59:45,590
裕仁天皇正式邀请我们访问日本
Emperor Hirohito has officially invited us to Japan.

863
01:59:47,050 --> 01:59:49,090
我将单独去
I'm going alone.

864
01:59:49,180 --> 01:59:51,550
你呆在这里
You are staying here

865
01:59:51,640 --> 01:59:53,970
我再也不会去日本
I will never go to Japan.

866
01:59:54,060 --> 01:59:56,060
那回你的房间去
Then go to your room.

867
02:00:03,020 --> 02:00:06,030
皇上万岁！
Ten thousand years to His Majesty the Emperor!

868
02:00:07,860 --> 02:00:10,240
- 万岁！ - 万岁！
- Ten thousand years! - Ten thousand years!

869
02:00:10,320 --> 02:00:14,830
皇上万岁！
Ten thousand years to His Majesty, the Emperor!

870
02:00:14,910 --> 02:00:18,120
万岁！
Ten thousand years! 

871
02:00:22,750 --> 02:00:24,670
万岁！
Ten thousand years!

872
02:00:29,840 --> 02:00:34,550
万岁！ 万岁！
Ten thousand years! Ten thousand years!

873
02:01:19,730 --> 02:01:22,730
告诉你 我恨你
I told you I hate you.

874
02:01:25,230 --> 02:01:28,230
只是因为我满足你一切吗
Only because I give you what you need.

875
02:02:02,640 --> 02:02:04,560
我们现在是一对了
Now we're engaged.

876
02:03:00,870 --> 02:03:03,870
- 你忘了我的牙粉 - 哦
- You forgot my tooth powder. - oh.

877
02:03:03,950 --> 02:03:05,960
是的 先生
Yes, sir.

878
02:03:24,600 --> 02:03:26,600
换掉他
Move him.

879
02:03:31,110 --> 02:03:33,320
981号！收拾你的东西！
981 , collect your things

880
02:03:43,200 --> 02:03:45,200
上楼！
Upstairs!

881
02:03:49,380 --> 02:03:51,380
站住！
Stop.

882
02:03:59,090 --> 02:04:02,050
你的鞋带开了 系好！
Your laces are undone. Do them up.

883
02:04:02,140 --> 02:04:05,430
星期四 你准备午餐 星期五 打扫洗漱间
Thursday you serve lunch. Friday you clean the toilet.

884
02:04:05,520 --> 02:04:07,680
星期天 打扫走廊
Saturday you sweep the floor.

885
02:04:35,340 --> 02:04:38,420
我从未和家人分开过
I have never been separated from my family.

886
02:04:38,510 --> 02:04:40,680
你最好能习惯！
You'd better get used to it.

887
02:04:45,600 --> 02:04:48,020
你不记得我了 是不是？
You do not remember me, do you?

888
02:04:48,100 --> 02:04:51,640
我是满洲国的贸易部长
I was the minister of trade in Manchukuo.

889
02:04:55,690 --> 02:04:57,860
你们都在满洲国
You were all in Manchukuo.

890
02:04:59,860 --> 02:05:01,780
现在 我是狱头
Now I am the cell leader.

891
02:05:01,860 --> 02:05:06,330
在这里守规矩很重要 学习时不要讲话
It is important to follow the rules here. No talking during study sessions.

892
02:05:59,670 --> 02:06:01,590
你的枪呢 队长？
Where is your gun, Captain?

893
02:06:01,670 --> 02:06:03,590
他们的剑呢？
Where are their swords?

894
02:06:03,680 --> 02:06:06,180
我们的武器被收了 皇上
Our weapons have been removed, Your Majesty...

895
02:06:06,260 --> 02:06:08,930
根据吉冈町上校的命令
on the orders of Colonel Yoshioka.

896
02:06:09,010 --> 02:06:11,310
吉冈町上校？
Colonel Yoshioka?

897
02:06:12,810 --> 02:06:16,190
- 吉冈町上校 - 这里发生了什么？
- Colonel Yoshioka. - What has happened here?

898
02:06:16,270 --> 02:06:18,480
为什么我的卫兵被缴械？
Why has my guard been disarmed?

899
02:06:18,570 --> 02:06:21,070
非常不幸 皇上
Yes, it is very unfortunate, Your Majesty.

900
02:06:21,150 --> 02:06:24,070
自从你去了东京 这里发生了许多变化
There have been many changes while you were in Tokyo.

901
02:06:24,150 --> 02:06:27,820
皇上 我向您介绍Masaomi KobayaKawa
Your Majesty, may I present Masaomi Kobayakawa...

902
02:06:27,910 --> 02:06:31,790
日本驻满洲国新大使
the new Japanese ambassador to Manchukuo.

903
02:06:57,810 --> 02:07:00,940
为什么总理大臣郑孝胥不来接我？
Why is Prime Minister Hsiao Hsiu not here to receive me?

904
02:07:01,030 --> 02:07:04,280
总理大臣辞职了 皇上
The prime minister has resigned, Your Majesty.

905
02:07:04,360 --> 02:07:06,780
他的儿子被暗杀了
His son has been assassinated.

906
02:07:06,860 --> 02:07:08,780
暗杀了？
Assassinated?

907
02:07:08,870 --> 02:07:11,990
共匪干的 皇上
By Communist bandits, Your Majesty.

908
02:07:18,580 --> 02:07:20,750
我必须马上见他
I must see him at once.

909
02:07:20,840 --> 02:07:23,710
他拒绝见任何人 皇上
He refuses to see anyone, Your Majesty.

910
02:07:23,800 --> 02:07:26,260
他已经出家了
He has gone to a monastery...

911
02:07:26,340 --> 02:07:28,550
很远的地方
far away.

912
02:07:35,680 --> 02:07:38,190
你是谁？
Who are you?

913
02:07:38,270 --> 02:07:40,940
张景惠 皇上
Chang Chinghui, Your Majesty...

914
02:07:41,020 --> 02:07:43,440
国防大臣
Minister of Defense.

915
02:07:44,610 --> 02:07:46,610
是的
Yes.

916
02:07:48,280 --> 02:07:50,280
当然了
of course.

917
02:07:52,080 --> 02:07:55,330
议会4点开 皇上
The council meeting will be at 4:00, Your Majesty...

918
02:07:55,410 --> 02:07:57,710
国宴之前
before the state dinner.

919
02:08:08,590 --> 02:08:13,140
皇上必须签署这些文件
"The emperor has been asked to sign the following.

920
02:08:13,220 --> 02:08:15,140
在仔细考虑之后
"After careful consideration...

921
02:08:15,220 --> 02:08:18,730
我们决定提名张景惠…
"we have decided to nominate the Honorable Chang Chinghui...

922
02:08:18,810 --> 02:08:22,310
当满洲国的新总理大臣
as the new prime minister of Manchukuo."

923
02:08:27,780 --> 02:08:29,700
不
No.

924
02:08:29,780 --> 02:08:32,200
在我们从日本回来后的今天...
Today, on our return from Japan...

925
02:08:32,280 --> 02:08:35,990
我们想讲一些更重要的事情…
we wish to speak ofsomething more important...

926
02:08:36,080 --> 02:08:39,330
我们和日本友好关系的未来
the future of our friendship with Japan.

927
02:08:40,420 --> 02:08:43,920
这基于相互尊重之上
This is based on mutual respect.

928
02:08:44,000 --> 02:08:47,630
尊重意味着平等和独立
And respect means equality and independence.

929
02:08:47,710 --> 02:08:53,180
当两个皇帝站在一起 向两国国旗致敬时
When the two emperors stood together and saluted the two national flags...

930
02:08:53,260 --> 02:08:56,510
他们认识到满洲国的重要性(成年了)
they recognized that Manchukuo had come of age.

931
02:08:56,600 --> 02:08:59,980
满洲国不是殖民地  满洲国就是满洲
Manchukuo is not a colony. Manchukuo is Manchuria.

932
02:09:03,900 --> 02:09:06,230
两国之间的关系…
The relationship between our two countries...

933
02:09:06,320 --> 02:09:09,240
就象两个皇帝之间的关系
is like the relationship between its two emperors.

934
02:09:09,320 --> 02:09:11,740
它基于仁慈的信任
It is rooted in fraternal trust..

935
02:09:11,820 --> 02:09:13,740
来…
in...

936
02:09:13,820 --> 02:09:18,080
来实现保持我们古老传统的愿望
in the desire to preserve our ancient traditions...

937
02:09:18,160 --> 02:09:21,960
并且在相互尊重下保持我们的民族统一
and in a mutual respect for our national identities!

938
02:09:23,330 --> 02:09:26,250
我们已经迎来了一些大使…
Already we have welcomed the ambassadors...

939
02:09:26,340 --> 02:09:30,470
萨尔瓦多 哥斯达黎加 梵蒂冈
of El Salvador, Costa Rica the Vatican.

940
02:09:32,130 --> 02:09:35,760
我相信其他国家不久也会来的
Soon, I'm...I'm sure the other countries will follow.

941
02:09:54,820 --> 02:09:57,830
我怀孕了
I'm going to have a child.

942
02:10:01,160 --> 02:10:03,160
父亲是满洲人
The father is Manchurian.

943
02:10:08,670 --> 02:10:10,590
吉冈和甘粕先生
Colonel and Mr. Amakasu!

944
02:10:10,670 --> 02:10:12,670
我是为你做的！
I did it for you.

945
02:10:35,240 --> 02:10:38,950
皇上忘了签署新总理大臣任命！
His Majesty forgot to sign the appointment of the new prime minister...

946
02:10:39,030 --> 02:10:41,200
张景惠先生
Mr. Chang Chinghui.

947
02:10:42,250 --> 02:10:44,250
我没忘
I did not forget.

948
02:10:51,130 --> 02:10:53,300
当一个英国人抢劫某人时 皇上
When an Englishman robs someone, Your Majesty...

949
02:10:53,380 --> 02:10:55,590
他就成了一个绅士
he becomes a gentleman.

950
02:10:55,680 --> 02:10:59,430
如果他抢劫多人 他就成了骑士
If he robs a lot, he becomes a knight.

951
02:10:59,510 --> 02:11:03,850
你以为英国人把他们的帝国当成一个慈善团体？
Do you imagine the British run their empire as a charity?

952
02:11:03,930 --> 02:11:08,690
如果印度不得不为他的被占领付钱
If India has paid for the cost of its own occupation...

953
02:11:08,770 --> 02:11:11,070
那满洲国也必须付
so must Manchukuo!

954
02:11:24,960 --> 02:11:28,290
我们希望满洲国有个继承人
We hope Manchukuo will have an heir.

955
02:11:30,960 --> 02:11:33,000
皇后正怀孕
The empress is expecting a child.

956
02:11:33,090 --> 02:11:36,510
是的 皇上 我们明白这情况
Yes, Your Majesty. we are aware of the situation

957
02:11:42,890 --> 02:11:45,390
这是父亲的名字
This is the name of the father.

958
02:11:53,900 --> 02:11:56,530
他叫Chang！
His name is Chang

959
02:11:56,610 --> 02:11:58,610
他是你的司机
He is your driver.

960
02:12:17,380 --> 02:12:20,510
必要的证据都记录下来了
All the necessary facts have been recorded

961
02:12:20,590 --> 02:12:23,180
他要受到惩罚
The man will be punished.

962
02:12:23,260 --> 02:12:27,310
皇帝不允许他的尊严被玷污
The emperor cannot allow his honor to be stained.

963
02:12:43,660 --> 02:12:48,080
日本人是地球上唯一神圣的民族
The Japanese are the only divine race on earth.

964
02:12:48,160 --> 02:12:52,880
我们将占领中国  香港 印度尼西亚
We will take China, Hong Kong, Indochina...

965
02:12:52,960 --> 02:12:55,290
暹罗 马来西亚
Siam, Malaya...

966
02:12:55,380 --> 02:12:58,460
新加坡和印度！
Singapore and India!

967
02:12:58,550 --> 02:13:00,970
亚洲属于我们！
Asia belongs to us!

968
02:13:32,460 --> 02:13:35,460
你同屋的人对你有抱怨
There have been complaints from your cell mates.

969
02:13:35,540 --> 02:13:39,800
你必须学会夜里小便时不把别人搞醒！
You must learn how to urinate at night without waking them all up.

970
02:13:41,680 --> 02:13:46,600
方法是洒尿时顺着桶边…
The way to do it is to urinate against the side of the bucket...

971
02:13:46,680 --> 02:13:48,600
而不是尿到中间
not into the middle.

972
02:13:48,680 --> 02:13:50,680
是 同志
Yes, comrade

973
02:14:05,070 --> 02:14:08,080
你还以为我是你的仆人  是不是？
You still think I am your servant, don't you?

974
02:14:30,930 --> 02:14:33,350
你都是在假装
You are all pretending.

975
02:14:33,440 --> 02:14:35,850
你假装成你已经改正了
You are just pretending you have changed.

976
02:14:35,940 --> 02:14:40,020
住口！党会把我们教育成新人的！
Shut up! The party teaches us to be new men while working for a new China!

977
02:14:40,110 --> 02:14:42,820
你在甘粕的私人办公室工作
You worked in Amakasu's private office.

978
02:14:42,900 --> 02:14:46,910
你们还是原来的老样子！ 人不会改变
You are still the same people. People do not change.

979
02:14:46,990 --> 02:14:49,200
卫兵！卫兵！
Guard! Guard!

980
02:14:55,750 --> 02:14:57,670
卫兵！
Guard!

981
02:14:57,750 --> 02:15:00,460
- 是我造成的 - 卫兵！
- I let it happen. - Guard!

982
02:15:00,550 --> 02:15:03,550
- 卫兵！ - 是我造成的
- Guard! - I let it happen.

983
02:15:14,640 --> 02:15:16,640
噢！
Ohh! 

984
02:15:39,750 --> 02:15:42,170
第二个法令 皇上
The second edict, Your Majesty.

985
02:15:42,250 --> 02:15:46,090
日语将做满洲国学校的官方语言
Japanese will be the official language in Manchukuo schools.

986
02:15:57,190 --> 02:16:00,230
皇上！
Your Majesty!

987
02:16:05,070 --> 02:16:06,990
小孩生下来就死了 皇上
The baby was born dead, Your Majesty.

988
02:16:07,070 --> 02:16:09,320
皇后怎样？
How is the empress?

989
02:16:09,410 --> 02:16:12,370
如果她去诊所或暖和点的地方就好了
It will be better if she goes to a clinic, Somewhere warm.

990
02:16:16,290 --> 02:16:18,870
她已经离开了 皇上
She's already left, Your Majesty. 

991
02:17:10,760 --> 02:17:13,260
开门
Open the door.

992
02:18:12,820 --> 02:18:15,700
日本将满洲国牢牢地控制住后…
With Manchukuo now firmly in their grasp...

993
02:18:15,780 --> 02:18:19,450
不久就控制了中国北部的大部分地区
the Japanese soon controlled most of North China.

994
02:18:19,540 --> 02:18:22,910
1937年 他们做好了南攻的准备
By 1937 they were ready to strike south...

995
02:18:23,000 --> 02:18:25,710
对准了这个国家的心脏
at the heart of the country.

996
02:18:25,790 --> 02:18:30,500
进攻上海是历史上第一次对平民的轰炸
The attack on Shanghai was one of the first civilian bombing raids in history.

997
02:18:31,510 --> 02:18:34,930
它使千万人无家可归  千万人死去
It left thousands homeless, thousands dead.

998
02:18:40,890 --> 02:18:46,650
三个月以后 日本军队包围了南京的临时政府
Three months later, Japanese armies were besieging the provisional capital at Nanking...

999
02:18:46,730 --> 02:18:50,360
城市沦陷后 暴行开始了
and when the city fell the atrocities began.

1000
02:18:52,030 --> 02:18:56,240
为了恐吓中国的幸存者…
Trying to terrorize the rest of China into surrender...

1001
02:18:56,320 --> 02:18:59,200
日本最高统帅部命令的这场屠杀
the Japanese high command ordered a massacre.

1002
02:18:59,280 --> 02:19:03,870
2千多万平民被有系统地杀害
More than 200,000 civilians were systematically executed.

1003
02:19:03,960 --> 02:19:06,920
整个世界都看呆了
The world watched in horror..

1004
02:19:07,000 --> 02:19:09,170
但没人给予帮助
but no help was given.

1005
02:19:09,250 --> 02:19:12,590
1941年12月7日
On December 7, 1941...

1006
02:19:12,670 --> 02:19:16,970
日本袭击了 驻珍珠港的美国舰队
Japan attacked the American fleet at Pearl Harbor.

1007
02:19:17,050 --> 02:19:18,890
没有事先警告
There was no warning.

1008
02:19:19,930 --> 02:19:23,720
满洲国 日本在中国东北的基地…
Manchukuo, the Japanese bastion in North China...

1009
02:19:23,810 --> 02:19:27,270
仍被傀儡皇帝溥仪统治
was still ruled by the puppet emperor Pu Yi.

1010
02:19:29,020 --> 02:19:31,570
但是在成功的背后…
But behind the facade oftriumph...

1011
02:19:31,650 --> 02:19:35,070
是一个国家的被奴役…
was a country enslaved...

1012
02:19:35,150 --> 02:19:39,660
在这个国家 日本进行了细菌战…
a country where Japanese experiments in biological warfare...

1013
02:19:39,740 --> 02:19:43,700
进行了活体实验…
were carried out on live human beings...

1014
02:19:43,790 --> 02:19:49,250
在这个国家 鸦片的种植成了资助战争最廉价的方式
a country where opium production became the easiest way to finance the war.

1015
02:19:51,040 --> 02:19:54,880
数百万人被故意地诱导成吸毒者
Millions of people were deliberately turned into drug addicts.

1016
02:20:20,030 --> 02:20:24,200
广岛原子弹爆炸后的第9天…
Nine days after the bomb at Hiroshima...

1017
02:20:24,290 --> 02:20:27,660
即1945年8月15日…
on August 15, 1945...

1018
02:20:27,750 --> 02:20:31,580
裕仁天皇宣布日本投降
Emperor Hirohito announced the surrender ofJapan.

1019
02:20:32,630 --> 02:20:36,760
他的声音第一次出现在收音机中
It was the first time his voice had ever been heard on radio.

1020
02:21:21,300 --> 02:21:23,720
你必须去东京 皇上
You must get to Tokyo, Your Majesty

1021
02:21:23,800 --> 02:21:26,430
你必须向美国投降 而不是向俄国人
You must surrender to the Americans, not the Russians.

1022
02:21:26,510 --> 02:21:29,020
共产党会杀了所有的人
The Communists will kill everyone.

1023
02:22:14,440 --> 02:22:16,980
皇后回来了
The empress has returned.

1024
02:22:24,240 --> 02:22:26,740
皇上 请
Majesty, please.

1025
02:22:31,870 --> 02:22:33,870
皇上！
Your Majesty!

1026
02:23:26,880 --> 02:23:29,850
快！飞机上没地方了 皇上！
Hurry! There is no room on the plane, Your Majesty!

1027
02:23:29,930 --> 02:23:33,430
女人没有危险！ 我们要快！
The women are not in danger! we must hurry!

1028
02:24:29,700 --> 02:24:32,910
皇上！皇上现在要走！
Your Majesty! Your Majesty is leaving now!

1029
02:24:32,990 --> 02:24:34,990
现在！
Now!

1030
02:25:10,490 --> 02:25:12,490
俄国人！
The Russians!

1031
02:25:50,650 --> 02:25:55,370
你以为我们在这里是为了教人们撒谎的新办法
Perhaps you think we are here to teach men to lie in a new way

1032
02:25:55,450 --> 02:25:58,830
为什么所有对你的指控 你都承认？
Why did you sign every accusation made against you?

1033
02:25:58,910 --> 02:26:02,580
我不想看到你象要自杀的样子…
I didn't stop you from killing yourself to see you like this...

1034
02:26:03,580 --> 02:26:08,250
一个为取媚于敌人什么都签署的人  又取媚于我！
someone who signs anything to please his enemies, to please me!

1035
02:26:08,340 --> 02:26:11,590
你知道满洲国的很多事情…
You knew about a lot of things in Manchukuo...

1036
02:26:11,670 --> 02:26:13,930
甚至秘密协议…
even the secret agreement...

1037
02:26:14,010 --> 02:26:15,930
但是你并不能知道…
but you couldn't possibly have known...

1038
02:26:16,010 --> 02:26:19,640
日本人在哈尔滨进行的细菌战实验！
about theJapanese biological warfare experiments in Harbin.

1039
02:26:19,720 --> 02:26:21,730
你能吗？
Could you?

1040
02:26:23,060 --> 02:26:26,400
为什么你承认这些呢？
So why did you sign these papers?

1041
02:26:30,490 --> 02:26:32,900
我对所有的事负责
I was responsible for everything.

1042
02:26:32,990 --> 02:26:35,660
你对你所做的事负责！
You are responsible for what you do!

1043
02:26:36,910 --> 02:26:39,990
在你一生中 你以为你比任何人优越
All your life you thought you were better than everyone else.

1044
02:26:40,080 --> 02:26:43,080
现在你认为你比任何人倒霉！
Now you think you are the worst of all!

1045
02:26:48,960 --> 02:26:51,300
为什么不让我独处一会？
Why can you not leave me alone?

1046
02:26:53,630 --> 02:26:57,930
你救我是为了让我在你的游戏中当木偶
You saved my life to make me a puppet in your own play.

1047
02:26:58,010 --> 02:27:00,930
你救我是因为我对你有用
You saved me because I am useful to you.

1048
02:27:01,020 --> 02:27:04,100
那么可怕…
Is that so terrible...

1049
02:27:04,190 --> 02:27:06,440
为了有用？
to be useful?

1050
02:27:38,890 --> 02:27:40,600
爱新觉罗・溥仪
Aisin-Gioro Pu Yi.

1051
02:27:45,520 --> 02:27:50,560
最高人民法院令…
By order of the Supreme People's Court...

1052
02:27:50,650 --> 02:27:54,900
战犯爱新觉罗溥仪…
the war criminal Aisin-Gioro Pu Yi...

1053
02:27:54,990 --> 02:27:58,410
男 53岁…
male, 53 years old...

1054
02:27:58,490 --> 02:28:00,990
满洲人…
of the Manchu nationality...

1055
02:28:01,080 --> 02:28:02,990
来自北京…
and from Peking...

1056
02:28:03,080 --> 02:28:06,040
现已拘押了10年！
has now served 10 years' detention.

1057
02:28:06,120 --> 02:28:11,170
在其关押期间经过劳动思想改造…
As a result of remolding through labor...

1058
02:28:11,250 --> 02:28:15,840
和意识形态方面的教育…
and ideological education during his captivity...

1059
02:28:15,920 --> 02:28:19,340
用行动证明了他已改过自新！
he has shown that he has genuinely reformed.

1060
02:28:19,430 --> 02:28:25,020
根据特赦令中的条款…
In accordance with clause one of the Special Pardon order...

1061
02:28:25,100 --> 02:28:29,140
他被特赦
he is therefore to be released

1062
02:28:40,200 --> 02:28:42,120
你明白？
You see?

1063
02:28:42,200 --> 02:28:46,240
我会在监狱待得比你长
I will end up living in prison longer than you.

1064
02:31:19,020 --> 02:31:22,530
红卫兵
The Red Guards. 

1065
02:31:28,320 --> 02:31:30,330
他们那么年轻
They are so young.

1066
02:31:31,660 --> 02:31:33,750
那很危险
It is dangerous.

1067
02:31:39,960 --> 02:31:41,710
看
Look.

1068
02:31:41,800 --> 02:31:44,800
那儿 蒲节 看！
Over there. Pu Chieh, look!

1069
02:31:48,220 --> 02:31:51,050
是我们的监狱长！
It is the governor of our prison!

1070
02:31:51,140 --> 02:31:53,060
- 不会的！ - 是的！
- It cannot be. - It is!

1071
02:31:53,140 --> 02:31:55,060
我肯定是的！
I'm sure it is!

1072
02:31:57,560 --> 02:31:59,560
小心！
Be careful.

1073
02:32:00,860 --> 02:32:03,530
回来！
Come back!

1074
02:32:46,990 --> 02:32:50,030
同志这肯定是个误会！
Comrade, this must be a mistake.

1075
02:32:50,110 --> 02:32:52,410
我认识这个人！他是个好人
I know this man. He is a good man.

1076
02:32:52,490 --> 02:32:55,410
- 你是谁？ - 我是个花匠
- Who are you? - I am a gardener.

1077
02:32:55,490 --> 02:32:58,500
加入我们 同志 否则走开！
Join us, comrade, or fuck off!

1078
02:33:07,720 --> 02:33:09,630
但他做了什么？
But what has he done?

1079
02:33:09,720 --> 02:33:12,220
- 他被指控 - 指控什么？
- He has been accused. - Accused of what?

1080
02:33:12,300 --> 02:33:14,260
- 帝国主义者！- 反革命分子！
- Emperor's lackey! - Revisionist element!

1081
02:33:14,350 --> 02:33:16,470
叛国者！
Rotten rightist!

1082
02:33:16,560 --> 02:33:19,480
- 交待你的罪行！ - 我没什么要交待的
- Confess your crime. - I have nothing to confess.

1083
02:33:19,560 --> 02:33:21,310
向毛主席磕头
Kowtow to Chairman Mao.

1084
02:33:25,230 --> 02:33:28,190
- 交待你的罪行！ - 我没什么要交待的
- Confess your crimes. - I have nothing to confess.

1085
02:33:28,280 --> 02:33:30,030
磕头！
Kowtow!

1086
02:33:33,370 --> 02:33:35,990
- 交待你的罪行！ - 等等！
- Confess your crimes! - Wait!

1087
02:33:36,080 --> 02:33:39,000
他是个老师！ 他是个好老师！
He's a teacher! He is a good teacher!

1088
02:33:39,080 --> 02:33:42,420
- 你们不能这样对他！ - 滚！滚！
- You...You cannot do this to him! - Move! Move!

1089
02:33:42,500 --> 02:33:45,500
你们错了！ 他是个好老师！
You are wrong! He is a good teacher!

1090
02:36:47,100 --> 02:36:50,020
站住！
Stop!

1091
02:36:50,100 --> 02:36:53,730
你不许到那里！
You are not allowed in there!

1092
02:36:57,110 --> 02:36:59,030
- 你是谁？ - 我住这里
- Who are you? - I live here.

1093
02:36:59,110 --> 02:37:01,030
我是花匠的儿子！
I am the son of the guardian.

1094
02:37:01,120 --> 02:37:03,740
是吗 我原来也住这里
Ah, well, I used to live here too.

1095
02:37:03,830 --> 02:37:07,750
- 我原来就坐那里 - 你是谁？
- That is where I sat. - who are you?

1096
02:37:07,830 --> 02:37:10,620
我原是中国的皇帝
I was the emperor of China.

1097
02:37:10,710 --> 02:37:12,710
证明呢！
Prove it!

1098
02:38:51,890 --> 02:38:54,310
这里是太和殿…
This is the Hall of Supreme Harmony...

1099
02:38:54,390 --> 02:38:56,310
皇帝加冕的地方
where the emperors were crowned.

1100
02:38:56,400 --> 02:39:00,320
在这里加冕的最后一个皇帝是爱新觉罗・溥仪
The last emperor to be crowned here was Aisin-Gioro Pu Yi.

1101
02:39:00,400 --> 02:39:02,320
他那时3岁
He was three years old.